From full truckload shipments to specialized logistics, USKO stands as a trusted partner in comprehensive logistics and cargo management across North America and Europe.

Our premium white-glove service ensures your high-value equipment and sensitive technology arrives safely, on time, every time, with TSA certified drivers ensuring maximum security.

, // Transportation Assets

Our Transportation Assets

Comprehensive Fleet Solutions for Every Need

Express LTL & Full Truckload

  • 150+ company-owned tractors for reliable capacity
  • Dedicated team drivers for high-value, time-sensitive shipments
  • Specialized 53' trailers with air-ride suspension and logistics bars
  • Temperature-controlled solutions for sensitive electronics
  • 24/7 tracking via satellite GPS with real-time monitoring

Expedite White Glove Services

USKO specialized lift gate service for precision delivery

  • Extensive fleet of box trucks with lift gates for specialized deliveries
  • High-performance sprinter vans for time-critical deliveries
  • TSA certified drivers for secure transportation of high-value goods
  • Custom handling equipment for fragile IT hardware and servers

Why Choose USKO for Geodis/IBM?

Security First

Our TSA certified drivers and secure chain of custody ensure your valuable IT assets are protected at every step.

Tech Expertise

Specialized equipment and trained personnel for handling sensitive electronics and server equipment.

Global Reach

Seamless cross-border operations through our Monterrey branch and established European network.

, // Network Coverage - Updated to just list branches

Our Branch Network

Strategic Locations Across North America and Europe

United States

  • Rancho Cordova, CA Branch
  • West Sacramento, CA Branch
  • Sacramento, CA Warehouse
  • Chicago, IL Branch
  • St Marys, GA Branch
  • Houston, TX Branch

Europe

  • Warsaw, Poland Branch
  • Kyiv, Ukraine Branch
  • Odesa, Ukraine Branch

Latin America

  • Monterrey, Mexico Branch
  • Daily cross-border operations with the US

The Sacramento Warehouse provides 85,000 sq ft of dry storage and 35,000 sq ft of refrigerated storage capacity. All USKO branches are strategically positioned to provide optimal coverage for Geodis/IBM shipments.

, // Sacramento Warehouse Capacity - New Slide

Sacramento Warehouse Capacity

State-of-the-Art Storage Facilities for Dry and Refrigerated Goods

Dry Storage Warehouse

Total Capacity: 85,000 sq ft
  • High-bay racking with 24,000 pallet positions
  • Advanced warehouse management system
  • 24/7 security monitoring and access control
  • 12 dock doors with automated levelers
  • Cross-docking capabilities for efficient transfers

Refrigerated Storage Facility

Total Capacity: 35,000 sq ft
  • Temperature zones: -10F to 55F capability
  • Redundant cooling systems with backup generators
  • Real-time temperature monitoring systems
  • 6 specialized refrigerated dock doors
  • FDA and USDA compliant facilities

Value-Added Warehouse Services

Inventory Management

Real-time tracking, cycle counting, and customized inventory reports with detailed analytics.

Order Fulfillment

Pick and pack services, custom labeling, kitting, and direct-to-consumer shipping capabilities.

IT Integration

API connections with Geodis/IBM systems for seamless order processing and inventory visibility.

, // Geodis/IBM Custom Slide

Partnering with Geodis & IBM

Custom Logistics Solutions for Your Business

Our Value Proposition

  • Secure IT Equipment Transportation

    TSA certified drivers and specialized handling procedures for servers, network equipment, and sensitive electronics.

  • Cross-Border Expertise

    Seamless movement of IT assets between US and Mexico through our new Monterrey branch, with customs clearance expertise.

  • White Glove Service

    Specialized lift gate equipment, inside delivery, unpacking, and debris removal for data center equipment and server installations.

  • Transparent Documentation

    Comprehensive chain of custody records, detailed proof of delivery, and real-time tracking for all shipments.

Key Benefits for Geodis/IBM

Time-Definite Delivery

99.3% on-time performance for critical IT equipment deployments

Risk Mitigation

Specialized handling reduces damage claims to less than 0.5%

Scalable Capacity

Dedicated fleet ensures availability during high-demand periods

Regulatory Compliance

TSA certified teams ensuring security protocols are followed

Did You Know?

USKO's new Monterrey branch specializes in cross-border logistics between the US and Mexico, with dedicated TSA certified drivers and customs specialists to ensure seamless IT equipment transportation for multinational operations.

, // DoD Approved Transportation Slide

DoD Approved Transportation Services

Supporting Your Military and Defense Logistics Requirements

DoD Approved Transportation Service Provider

USKO is proud to be an approved DoD Transportation Service Provider (TSP), fully equipped to handle the specialized requirements of your military shipments.

Our experience working with defense contractors like IBM enables us to deliver secure, compliant, and on-time transportation services for your most sensitive military logistics needs.

  • COMSEC-approved drivers and handling procedures
  • Expert navigation of MFTURP and other military transportation systems
  • Familiar with military base access protocols and requirements
  • Transportation services compliant with NISPOM and ITAR regulations

Our Military Logistics Expertise

Security Clearances

Our drivers maintain appropriate security clearances for transporting sensitive defense materials and equipment.

Scheduling Expertise

We understand the unique scheduling requirements of military logistics and ensure precise coordination with base personnel.

Geodis/IBM Military Support

We can help Geodis/IBM fulfill defense contracts with reliable transportation for military IT equipment and systems.

Chain of Custody

Rigorous documentation and tracking systems ensure unbroken chain of custody for defense-related shipments.

Experience You Can Trust

USKO has successfully handled countless military shipments, providing reliable transportation services for defense contractors and government agencies across North America.

Our team understands the critical nature of military logistics and can work with Geodis/IBM to ensure your defense-related deliveries meet all security and compliance requirements.

, // Closing Slide

Ready to Transform Your Logistics Experience?

Partner with USKO to elevate Geodis/IBM's transportation capabilities with our specialized fleet, TSA certified teams, and DoD-approved security protocols.
